title: Easytrip Web Admin
description: An administration website for the Easytrip Mobile App. Where, admins can monitor their customer counts, customer registrations, vehicle registrations on a daily, weekly, monthly or yearly view. This site also have a list for users, vehicles, advertisements that is presented in a table format. There is also a view per user & vehicle where the admin can see all of its information and admin can also transfer registered vehicles to other users for whatever reason.
